    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Nations whose residents, or some portion thereof, exercise self-government, and usually but not always hold sovereignty over the territory. To specifically designate independent nations having sovereignty, use "independent sovereign nations."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
